    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>咕咕呱噗乐</strong>是一款主打一个混乱搞怪的1v1宅家派对格斗游戏。把MOBA策略和超能宝宝的疯狂技能融为一体，拿起手柄，和朋友面对面，来一场超燃的对战吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/c36954a0f6a8a107319e476839dfca1f.poster.avif?t=1767822584\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/c36954a0f6a8a107319e476839dfca1f.webm?t=1767822584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在商店里随心升级你的宝宝！每场比赛，升级各种技能解锁全新成长路线！想用<i>黏黏手</i>把对手从竞技场另一端拽过来？尽管放手去玩！想用<i>积木</i>绊倒他们？没问题！不管是发射<i>弹力球</i>还是召唤爆炸<i>遥控车</i>，每场对决都是一次智斗的新机会！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/d2fb995a2df23e32d2f56a6213a26233.poster.avif?t=1767822584\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/d2fb995a2df23e32d2f56a6213a26233.webm?t=1767822584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入这个玩具战场，你会发现每件玩具都代表一种新策略。看看谁能在对手之前打造出终极宝宝战士！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/1e73ba149e09d028ee75883c0bef9d5f.poster.avif?t=1767822584\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/1e73ba149e09d028ee75883c0bef9d5f.webm?t=1767822584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MOBA 机制：</strong>推进兵线、争夺地图目标、击败你的对手</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强化你的宝宝：</strong>组合各种攻击与被动技能，打造数百种独特配置</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>翻盘逆袭：</strong>在背水一战中扭转战局！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本地多人对战：</strong>智能分屏，让近距离对战更加紧张刺激</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多张地图：</strong>在多路和单路地图上展开激烈战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>训练模式：</strong>自由实验，按自己的节奏掌握技巧</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>模拟控制：</strong>精准的双摇杆瞄准与移动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自由选择操作方式：</strong>无论是键盘鼠标还是手柄，选择适合你的操作方式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>原创配乐：</strong>多位艺术家带来的劲爆音轨</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/323e773f442fc15b92b6f553bc169620.apng?t=1767822584\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/323e773f442fc15b92b6f553bc169620.poster.avif?t=1767822584\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=96 /></picture></span></p>",
